[{"count": 0, "tags": [], "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "attachment_id": null, "text": "I have set ANT_HOME=/cygdrive/c/ant in my Cygwin environment\n\n\nthis is fine for cygwin, it means C:\\ant in Windows linguo\n\n\n\n\nNow when I do a build.sh install, my software gets installed under\n\n\nC:\\cygdrive\\c\\ant which is not what I wanted\n\n\n\n\nI am going to add a patch to the report.", "id": 31693, "time": "2003-02-20T19:10:29Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-02-20T19:10:29Z", "is_private": false}, {"count": 1, "tags": [], "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "attachment_id": 4938, "text": "Created attachment 4938\npatch for build.sh", "id": 31694, "time": "2003-02-20T19:11:01Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-02-20T19:11:01Z", "is_private": false}, {"count": 2, "text": "Created attachment 4939\npatch for build.sh", "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "attachment_id": 4939, "id": 31695, "time": "2003-02-20T19:12:22Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-02-20T19:12:22Z", "tags": [], "is_private": false}, {"count": 3, "tags": [], "bug_id": 17257, "attachment_id": 4940, "id": 31696, "time": "2003-02-20T19:12:50Z", "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "creation_time": "2003-02-20T19:12:50Z", "is_private": false, "text": "Created attachment 4940\npatch for build.sh"}, {"count": 4, "tags": [], "bug_id": 17257, "attachment_id": 4941, "id": 31697, "time": "2003-02-20T19:13:45Z", "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "creation_time": "2003-02-20T19:13:45Z", "is_private": false, "text": "Created attachment 4941\npatch for build.sh"}, {"count": 5, "tags": [], "creator": "conor@apache.org", "attachment_id": null, "text": "Shouldn't this be something like\n\ncygpath --path --windows \"$ANT_HOME\n\nas is done in the ant script?", "id": 31745, "time": "2003-02-21T11:44:19Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-02-21T11:44:19Z", "is_private": false}, {"count": 6, "text": "Yes, Conor, go ahead with\n\n\n  if $cygwin; then\n\n\n  REALANTHOME=`cygpath --path --windows \"$REALANTHOME\"`\n\n\n  fi\n\n\n", "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "attachment_id": null, "id": 31750, "time": "2003-02-21T12:13:23Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-02-21T12:13:23Z", "tags": [], "is_private": false}, {"count": 7, "tags": [], "bug_id": 17257, "attachment_id": null, "id": 31751, "time": "2003-02-21T12:16:49Z", "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "creation_time": "2003-02-21T12:16:49Z", "is_private": false, "text": "I have just read that --path for things which are not paths create problems, so\n\n\n if $cygwin; then\n\n\n  REALANTHOME=`cygpath --windows \"$REALANTHOME\"`\n\n\nfi\n"}, {"count": 8, "tags": [], "creator": "levylambert@tiscali-dsl.de", "attachment_id": null, "text": "change submitted", "id": 35261, "time": "2003-04-15T19:59:20Z", "bug_id": 17257, "creation_time": "2003-04-15T19:59:20Z", "is_private": false}]